      "dialog": {
        "dialogName": "USBStick",
        "trigger": 0,
        "character": 1,
        "lines": [
          "ohhh, you're already here?",
          "You will now learn about a new element!",
          "The DEFENDERS!",
          "As you will see, the defenders are just elements that will guard a system.",
          "you should learn to avoid them, because they can be quite annoying - especially in systems with a time limit!",
          "As you will see, touching them will cause you to walk slower!",
          "and on top of it...",
          "if you hold a laptop they will make you drop the laptop and reset its hack color!",
          "This will lead to situations where you have to be extra cautious when going fast, in order to reach the data in time.",
          "i will now let you find out about them yourself.",
          "have fun!"
        ]
